text: Dallas' place was great. It was clean and had updated finishings. We had a group of 9 girls staying in his condo and surprisingly all 9 of us had room and were comfortable. The condo is a convenient 10 minute cab ride to downtown. There were plenty of bath towels and blankets for everyone. Dallas was friendly and helpful if we had any questions throughout our stay.
title: Excellent Proximity Austin 4bd 3ba
